    "description": "Whether or not you love peanut butter, you'll definitely go nuts for this dish! You'll combine peanut butter, chilli jam, soy and coconut cream to make a nutty sauce to drizzle all over charred broccoli & roasted pork. Served with brown rice for a satay-inspired supper!",
